We recommended and Management agreed to the following:
a. Provide funding for the projects affected by the relocation of facilities of
electric cooperative pursuant to R.A. 10531 and Joint Circular No. 01
series of 2017 of DOE and DPWH;
b. Secure the deed of donation of the identified location of the project to
enforce implementation;
c. Secure funding for the water test requirement of the Mines and
Geoscience Bureau for the water system projects;
d. Expedite the construction of infrastructure projects;
e. Impose liquidated damages on the projects which are not completed within the
targeted date of completion;
f. Comply with the provisions of the Revised IRR of RA 9184 on the
termination of contracts. Ensure that projects will be completed after the
termination is made; and
g. Return the excess funds from the completed projects to the source
agencies.

